part that would make it a dipole."
>>>
>>> BUT, an end fed, resonant half wave vertical dipole DOES have 'the othe=
r half of
>>> the antenna' =85 'the part that would make it a dipole'.
>>>
>>> I'd accept the generalization for antennas which are NOT dipoles but I =
have
>>> problems with it as a universal truth.
